    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eighthwell is a story-rich action-adventure game packed with humour and charm. Play as the lost boy, Oscar, as you explore Eighthwell, a quirky town full of strange residents and even stranger secrets. Battle enemies in shooter style combat as you traverse unique dungeons with your new friends. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/0a15fd7a0eb4bf17936fc38dd1fc1f16.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/0a15fd7a0eb4bf17936fc38dd1fc1f16.webm?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/0a15fd7a0eb4bf17936fc38dd1fc1f16.mp4?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> &quot;Wow, a stranger.&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/4cdfa0b30c389652329cb27f117b90cd.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" width=600 height=89 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/4cdfa0b30c389652329cb27f117b90cd.webm?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full of unique and quirky characters to meet</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of charming locations to visit, each with their own distinct look and feel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeons crawling with enemies and puzzles to traverse</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of terrible jokes to find</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/74a6f8a1128b44a14865498d2e358abd.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" width=568 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/74a6f8a1128b44a14865498d2e358abd.webm?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/74a6f8a1128b44a14865498d2e358abd.mp4?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/aa9bbe20dbac9ab209f832bb4502eec4.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" width=600 height=108 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/aa9bbe20dbac9ab209f832bb4502eec4.webm?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle an assortment of enemy types, each with a unique design and attack pattern</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge and weave through enemy projectiles while firing back with your own magic bullets in twin-stick shooter style combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new useful abilities as you progress through the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting boss battles to challenge</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/0abaee4a57caacaf064c2e9d587e2424.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" width=568 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/0abaee4a57caacaf064c2e9d587e2424.webm?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/0abaee4a57caacaf064c2e9d587e2424.mp4?t=1730571858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/d646151590d8fd3645659e3e2c6bdcbb.webp?t=1730571858\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/d646151590d8fd3645659e3e2c6bdcbb.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=108 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A handcrafted original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pet a…sheep?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Football, sandwiches and vandalism…?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/25d9076b2655057bce14cdd7d58af0e0.apng?t=1730571858\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258250/extras/25d9076b2655057bce14cdd7d58af0e0.poster.avif?t=1730571858\" class=\"bb_img\" width=550 height=320 /></picture></span></p>",
